{"ID":"20241031175141-u6xxplh","Spec":"1","Type":"NodeDocument","Properties":{"id":"20241031175141-u6xxplh","title":"Kubernetes基础概念","type":"doc","updated":"20241107103434"},"Children":[{"ID":"20241107103431-ttspve3","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20241107103431-ttspve3","updated":"20241107103434"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"官方参考文档"}]},{"ID":"20241107103426-35wuojf","Type":"NodeCodeBlock","IsFencedCodeBlock":true,"Properties":{"id":"20241107103426-35wuojf","updated":"20241107103428"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeCodeBlockFenceOpenMarker","Data":"```"},{"Type":"NodeCodeBlockFenceInfoMarker","CodeBlockInfo":"c2hlbGw="},{"Type":"NodeCodeBlockCode","Data":"https://kubesphere.io/zh/docs/v3.3/pluggable-components/devops/\n"},{"Type":"NodeCodeBlockFenceCloseMarker","Data":"```"}]},{"ID":"20241031175207-jizat7r","Type":"NodeHeading","HeadingLevel":1,"Properties":{"id":"20241031175207-jizat7r","updated":"20241031175446"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"1、是什么"}]},{"ID":"20241031175211-ftf5plw","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20241031175211-ftf5plw","updated":"20241031175211"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"​"},{"Type":"NodeImage","Data":"span","Children":[{"Type":"NodeBang"},{"Type":"NodeOpenBracket"},{"Type":"NodeLinkText","Data":"image"},{"Type":"NodeCloseBracket"},{"Type":"NodeOpenParen"},{"Type":"NodeLinkDest","Data":"assets/image-20241031175211-rpphspw.png"},{"Type":"NodeCloseParen"}]},{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"​"}]},{"ID":"20241031175257-x7hkesj","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20241031175257-x7hkesj","updated":"20241031175259"}},{"ID":"20241031175300-pe6865v","Type":"NodeBlockquote","Properties":{"id":"20241031175300-pe6865v","updated":"20241031175303"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeBlockquoteMarker","Data":"\u003e"},{"ID":"20241031175303-odbube0","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20241031175303-odbube0","updated":"20241031175303"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"我们急需一个大规模容器编排系统"}]}]},{"ID":"20241031175300-45zp7z1","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20241031175300-45zp7z1","updated":"20241031175300"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"kubernetes具有以下特性：\n● 服务发现和负载均衡\nKubernetes 可以使用 DNS 名称或自己的 IP 地址公开容器，如果进入容器的流量很大， Kubernetes 可以负载均衡并分配网络流量，从而使部署稳定。\n● 存储编排\nKubernetes 允许你自动挂载你选择的存储系统，例如本地存储、公共云提供商等。\n● 自动部署和回滚\n你可以使用 Kubernetes 描述已部署容器的所需状态，它可以以受控的速率将实际状态 更改为期望状态。例如，你可以自动化 Kubernetes 来为你的部署创建新容器， 删除现有容器并将它们的所有资源用于新容器。\n● 自动完成装箱计算\nKubernetes 允许你指定每个容器所需 CPU 和内存（RAM）。 当容器指定了资源请求时，Kubernetes 可以做出更好的决策来管理容器的资源。\n● 自我修复\nKubernetes 重新启动失败的容器、替换容器、杀死不响应用户定义的 运行状况检查的容器，并且在准备好服务之前不将其通告给客户端。\n● 密钥与配置管理\nKubernetes 允许你存储和管理敏感信息，例如密码、OAuth 令牌和 ssh 密钥。 你可以在不重建容器镜像的情况下部署和更新密钥和应用程序配置，也无需在堆栈配置中暴露密钥。"}]},{"ID":"20241031175300-shhho26","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20241031175300-shhho26","updated":"20241031175446"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeTextMark","TextMarkType":"strong em","TextMarkTextContent":"Kubernetes 为你提供了一个可弹性运行分布式系统的框架。 Kubernetes 会满足你的扩展要求、故障转移、部署模式等。 例如，Kubernetes 可以轻松管理系统的 Canary 部署。"}]},{"ID":"20241031175300-4dqy7ao","Type":"NodeHeading","HeadingLevel":1,"Properties":{"id":"20241031175300-4dqy7ao","updated":"20241031175510"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"2、架构"}]},{"ID":"20241031175447-pusw3nz","Type":"NodeHeading","HeadingLevel":2,"Properties":{"id":"20241031175447-pusw3nz","updated":"20241031175510"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"1、工作方式"}]},{"ID":"20241031175506-43tps2w","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20241031175506-43tps2w","updated":"20241031175510"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeTextMark","TextMarkType":"strong","TextMarkTextContent":"Kubernetes Cluster = N Master Node + N Worker Node：N主节点+N工作节点； N\u0026gt;=1"},{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"\n\n"}]},{"ID":"20241031175504-ol9zfwh","Type":"NodeHeading","HeadingLevel":1,"Properties":{"id":"20241031175504-ol9zfwh","updated":"20241031180229"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"2、组件架构"}]},{"ID":"20241031175546-5o1ihlz","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20